<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a22Aug1938"><font color="red">22 August 1938</font> <i>MERC</i> (Jacques Mercanton memoir): Joyce in Lausanne with Nora and L&eacute;on &hellip; shows article in <i>Irish Times</i> on UCD &hellip; L&eacute;on going back &hellip; Mercanton asked to get <i>Le Rime</i> of Petrarch and <i>Epithalamion</i> of Spenser for use in I.8 and last pages of the book &ldquo;extra allusions to rivers&rdquo; &hellip; Joyce reading &ldquo;I Follow Saint Patrick&rdquo; </div>
